3 siu-nî (2011-2013) lóng-tsóng ki-tsat sîng-hāi hāi-sûng ê chi̍t-kè cash ki-tsat sī siáⁿ-mih?
Chiah-sī iâⁿ-lâi ū siōng koân ê chū-iâⁿ oa̍h-tāng chè-chō chîn-chū tōa-chā, hit tang ê chè-chū kap chè-chū téng-koân ê cheng-chē (chiap-siau) sī sím-mih?
2011 nian kàu 2013 nian, 'chū chok-gia̍p hoat-tōng chìn-chêng tit-tio̍h ê bōi suan-chè siâu' ê nian-kàu-nian piàn-hòa kah choân-thé kóng-hiòng sī siáⁿ-iūⁿ ê?
answer: Chū chok-gia̍p hoat-tōng chìn-chêng tit-tio̍h ê bōi suan-chè siâu chiān-chē ū siau-tû. I tùi 2011 nian kàu 2012 nian ( $20,963 kàu $18,884 ) kiam-chiām kiám-chió liáu $2,079 pah-bān Bí-kim, chiánhu chiū-chāi tùi 2012 nian kàu 2013 nian ( $18,884 kàu $20,776 ) tō-chòe piàn-choe̍h, ti̍t-kàu chha-put-to chha-put-to hūi-ho̍k kàu 2011 nian ê chu-liāu.

question: 2012 ni, 'tōa hōaⁿ chioh chha̍t chioh hōaⁿ chioh' hōaⁿ ê chìn chiah, hōaⁿ ê chìn chiah ê tùi tōa hōaⁿ ê hōaⁿ ê cha̍h

Nāi, nāi 2013 nî ê 'net cash used for investing activities' nāi nāi 20% koh-á-su, hit nî ê 'net increase (decrease) in cash and cash equivalents' ē-sī án-chóa-chē, lēng-gōa ê só͘-chāi lóng kāng-khó, nāi?
Tī chit ê saⁿ-nî kî-kan, chū chhiat-chok oa̍h-tāng só͘ tit-tio̍h ê chîⁿ kap chîⁿ chha-biat ê cheng-chha chha-biat ū chi̍t-ê kò͘-tēng ê koan-hē bē?
answer: Bōe, bōe chi̍t-ê kò͘-tēng ê koan-hē. Tī 2011 nî, siōng koân ê chhiat-chok chîⁿ-liû ($20,963M) hō͘ chîⁿ bôa-chú-chi̍t ê chha-biat ($-433M). Tī 2012 nî, siōng kē ê chhiat-chok chîⁿ-liû ($18,884M) hō͘ chîⁿ ū chi̍t-ê tōa ê cheng-chha ($3,413M). Chit-ê piáu-bī chò, tâu-chu kap oân-chiá oa̍h-tāng khah ū éng-hióng tī chîⁿ ê cheng-chha khah-kó chhiat-chok oa̍h-tāng chi̍t-ê.

question: Uì in-niâ ê 'chēng-kim-á-lâi chin chē (kiam kiám-chá) ê kim-ia̍h kap kim-gîn siūⁿ khoán-sû, koh ū ūi-chhin?
answer: 2012 sī chi̍t ê te̍k-sû ê nî-thâu, in-ūi sī choâⁿ-á hit tang ū chpositive ê chēng-kim-á-lâi chin chē kim-ia̍h kap kim-gîn (3,413 pah-bān ê kho͘-phiah), chi-áⁿ 2011 nî kap 2013 nî lóng sī kiám-chá (433 pah-bān ê kho͘-phiah kap 2,804 pah-bān ê kho͘-phiah, tùi-sìn).

question: 2011 nî ê sì chióng chiūⁿ-liû chi-oē tìn-sio̍h, chòe-chi̍t-ē 'lān-chòe (kē-chē) tī chiūⁿ-liû hām chiūⁿ-liû téng-bīn ê chiūⁿ-liû' lâi chhek-chèng pió-chàu ê kiàn-siat.
Nāi-suànn ê chū-chhap hoat-tōng-la̍k siu-jih tī 2013 nî pí 2012 nî tōa, m̄-koh tâu-chu tâu-la̍k siu-jih mā tōa, che kóng-bē 2013 nî ê kong-si chôan-thé cash koán-lí ū siánn-mih sū?
answer: Che kóng-bē tī 2013 nî ê kong-si tùi chū-chhap siu-jih ê chîⁿ pí 2012 nî koh tōa, i mā tâu-chu koh chē. Che piáu-bîng kong-si ē-tàng iōng koh chē ê chū-chhap sîu-la̍k lâi tōa tâu-chu ê hoat-tōng.
